== Amagambo n’interuro mu gicokitawu ==
* '''Chi hohchifo yat nanta?''' – Witwa nde?
* '''Sa hohchifo yat ... ''' – Nitwa ... 
* '''ofi''' &ndash; imbwa
* '''issoba/soba''' &ndash; ifarashi
* '''Hʊshi''' &ndash; Izuba

